<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><time_sig>S.M. (6.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<title>Thy kingdom come ƲIT106</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs pi̱ Mi̱ko ma!
 Auet pi̱ nukha̱klot,
 Pim anumpa ilbʋsha ya̱
 Ish haklo pullashke.

[V2]
 Ish apehlichika't
 Pim a̱ya pulla na,
 Chin tʋshka a̱hli fehna ka
 Ish pikbi pullashke.

[V3]
 Ish apehlichika't
 Yakni puta moma
 Hlopullit taiyahakbano,
 Il ahni fehnʋshke.

[V4]
 Ish apehlichika't
 Nan okpulo puta
 Mominchit imaiyachi na,
 Momʋt chimmi hashke.

[V5]
 Oklushi puta kʋt
 Chi haklo pulla cha,
 Ish apehlichika yoka
 Iba foyukashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Chisʋs pi̱ Mi̱ko ma!</aka>
<hymn_number>106</hymn_number>
<author>Captain Joseph Dukes</author>
</song>